# Weather App

## Description
A weather application that fetches current weather data for any city using the OpenWeatherMap API. This app displays temperature, weather conditions, and more.

## Features
- Fetch and display current weather data.
- Search weather by city name.
- Responsive design.

## Files
- `index.html`: The main HTML file that contains the structure of the Weather app.
- `styles.css`: The CSS file for styling the Weather app.
- `scripts.js`: The JavaScript file that handles the functionality of the Weather app.
